<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fancy HTML Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f6d365 0%, #fda085 100%);
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #f857a6;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #ff6f61;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to My Fancy Page</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Services</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>This is a Beautiful Page</h2>
        <p>
            This static page uses a combination of pleasing gradients, shadow effects, and clean typography to give it a modern and stylish look. It is fully responsive and works well on all screen sizes.
        </p>
        <p>
            You can further customize this template by adding more sections, images, and interactive elements as per your needs. Enjoy creating your fancy HTML page!
        </p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Â© 2024 Fancy HTML Page. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>

